{
  "stem": "1581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was put into the-- we-- we drew lots, and I was chosen to go into the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in this short time I was in the kitchen, we really revived because I could get some of my strength back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course I could feed my two friends, which were just as essential as myself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it bought us another few days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every day that we survived was a miracle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every day that we chalked up as survival was a success.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we had this reprieve.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day, our protector-- our guy in the Waffen SS-- obviously was found out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was put, probably, onto the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in this moment, the kapo of the kitchen who knew I was just put in by this guy, and he has other friends to put in there, I was given the most horrible beating I ever had in my life.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know whoever received a beating, but this beating hurt unbearably so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was the end of my kitchen adventure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our survival was dependent on a variety of miracles, or a chain of events, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] happenstances, luck, or whatever you want to call it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day, we were on a work outfit, and there was a-- a yell, is there a doctor around?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is there a doctor around?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, that was very suspicious because they use these tricks usually.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Is there somebody who knows to type?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or is there somebody who knows how to write?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or is there somebody who knows languages?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whenever somebody volunteered, they were given carrying corpses or cleaning latrines, or some kind of other occupation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I thought, well, I'll raise my hand.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
